Review:
Professional supplier of high quality stationary and office supplies, as well as everything for painters, artists, schools and children. Top floor is a really nice toy shop for kids.
Generally speaking here you will find everything you need for an office, art and kids.
Good store for all students and for official work. Alot of pens and notes and all what you want to do with paperwork
A nice stationary store who almost have all your requirements
You can find everything in this place! Love it
Very good variety and reasonable cost
Small flower shop at the petrol station with limited range of stock. OK for a quick stop but don't expect too much!
